      "title": "Step 2 - Upscale",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Upscale\n\nUsing Image Z Turbo on a low denoise value, we can increase detail in an image.\n\nCompared to a basic diffusion process a upscale uses lower denoising values.\n| Parameters  | Basic Diffusion | Upscaling |\n|--------|---------|------------\n| Ksampler: denoise  | 1.0     | 0.2 - 0.35         "
      ],
      "color": "#222",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
