      "title": "🔍 Core Concept",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Upscaling\n\nUpscaling increases image resolution and detail via diffusion, creating a higher-quality version that preserves original content and structure.\nIt adds denoised pixels throughout to enlarge the image, blending with the upscaled base for better clarity.\n\n## Automatic Image Analysis\n\nAutomatic image analysis with Florence-2 via Florence2Run to inspect the input image and create refined prompts for upscaling guidance.\nIt enhances the diffusion model with detailed descriptions of objects, textures, and contexts to improve results."
      ],
      "color": "#222",
      "bgcolor": "#000"
    }
